1
00:00:01,700 --> 00:00:03,700
Da.

2
00:00:03,900 --> 00:00:05,900
Sta nam je ciniti?

3
00:00:05,900 --> 00:00:07,600
Nadjimo ih.

4
00:00:07,700 --> 00:00:10,000
Da ih nadjemo? Gde?

5
00:00:12,700 --> 00:00:15,600
Niste gubili vreme
koliko vidim.

6
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:18,200
U ovo sam siguran.
Da li sam u pravu?

7
00:00:18,300 --> 00:00:20,300
Neko je medju nasima.

8
00:00:20,500 --> 00:00:22,700
O ne. Ali ko?

9
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:29,500
Neko saradjuje sa Brigadom.

10
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:32,745
Ili nas izdaje ili je previse iskren.

11
00:00:34,900 --> 00:00:37,200
Ta gospodjica Litvanova...

12
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:41,100
Mozda ste sa njom bili
previse iskreni?

13
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:43,200
Ja?

14
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:47,230
Sami ste pominjali
preveliku iskrenost?

15
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:50,990
Zao mi je. Da li
sumnjate u nekoga?

16
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:55,400
Moramo da porazgovaramo,
samo vi i ja.

17
00:00:55,500 --> 00:00:58,400
Naravno. Gde?

18
00:00:58,800 --> 00:01:01,095
Petrova kupaonica.
- U redu.

19
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:05,200
Tamo imaju odvojene sobe.
Sutra, u podne.

20
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:07,900
Soba 5.

21
00:01:09,700 --> 00:01:12,250
Tamo cemo sve
isterati na cisto

22
00:01:13,100 --> 00:01:15,100
U kupaonici?

23
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:18,600
Na cisto? Kako originalno.

24
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:22,000
Divim se vasoj originalnosti.

25
00:01:22,600 --> 00:01:27,400
Doci cu. I nemojte me prevariti.

26
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:29,500
U redu?

27
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:36,800
Kamcatka...

28
00:01:38,900 --> 00:01:41,200
Svi budite u mojoj kancelariji u podne.

29
00:01:41,300 --> 00:01:44,190
Pletete mrezu?
- Takav mi je posao.

30
00:01:44,900 --> 00:01:47,875
Da li cete doci na
sastanak u podne?

31
00:01:48,300 --> 00:01:51,700
Ne, grof Pozarski
i ja idemo u kupaonicu.

32
00:01:52,300 --> 00:01:55,955
Da operemo sitne misli,
da procistimo mozak.

33
00:01:56,100 --> 00:01:57,500
U Petrovu kupaonicu.

34
00:01:57,600 --> 00:02:01,680
Vise volim rusku verziju,
sa brezinim grancicama.

35
00:02:01,900 --> 00:02:04,195
Ruska verzija je varvarska.

36
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:07,500
Imam rezervaciju u sobi 1,
rimski stil.

37
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:11,850
Kada smo do toga, razgovaracu
sa njim danas u podne

38
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:17,300
u Petrovom kuplistu, soba dva.

39
00:02:18,900 --> 00:02:21,025
Samo, to je velika tajna.

40
00:02:21,900 --> 00:02:24,300
Naravno.

41
00:02:26,900 --> 00:02:29,000
Zavrsio sam.

42
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:37,100
Poznarski je rekao da ce
me poslati na Kamcatku.

43
00:02:37,500 --> 00:02:39,800
Idem danas sa njim u
Petrovu kupaonicu.

44
00:02:39,900 --> 00:02:41,800
Soba 3. Mogao bih
da kazem koju dobru za vas.

45
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:44,960
Beskorisno je. Molio
sam na kolenima.

46
00:02:45,500 --> 00:02:48,220
Radicu u Kamcatkanskoj policiji.

47
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:56,074
