48
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:16,360
Znaci, salju Burcinskog na Kamcatku.

49
00:03:16,700 --> 00:03:19,300
Zelite da saradjujem?

50
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:23,160
Drzavni savetnik je samo sitna riba.

51
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:26,900
Recite Pozarskom da cu
samo sa njim saradjivati

52
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,000
Da, nalazim se sa njim danas.

53
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:34,400
Petrova kupaonica, soba 3.

54
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:38,500
Najbolje mesto za
privatan razgovor.

55
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:44,000
Mala riba.

56
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,000
a?

57
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:57,800
Bicu u bazenu.

58
00:03:58,600 --> 00:03:59,900
Da.

59
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:04,900
Gledacu u koja vrata ce uci.

60
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:09,400
Koliko puta pokucam na vrata
broj 5 gde cete vi biti

61
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:11,880
znacice u koju sobu je usao.

62
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:13,900
Onda se vracam u bazen.

63
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,100
Da.

64
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:17,600
A soba 4?

65
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:22,600
Hteo sam da proverim Burcinskog
ali je izasao.

66
00:04:26,100 --> 00:04:28,100
Stizem.

67
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:41,300
Ulazi unutra!

68
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:43,500
Malo sam zauzet.

69
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:46,365
lonako danas idem u kupanicu.

70
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,600
Koju? - Petrovu.

71
00:04:48,700 --> 00:04:52,200
U podne se tamo sastajem
sa grofom Pozarskim.

72
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:55,600
Taj covek je bio osudjen
na revolucionarno pogubljenje.

73
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:58,100
Zasluzio je smrt.

74
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:07,900
Imamo rezervisano u sobi 4.

75
00:05:12,100 --> 00:05:14,200
Ne, zapravo 5.

76
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,600
Zao mi je. - Zao?

77
00:05:16,900 --> 00:05:20,895
Usudjujes se to da mi kazes?
Znam ja tvoj moral:

78
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:25,000
odvojene sobe sa gospodjicama
i kineskom masazom.

79
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:27,225
Dodaj mi cebe nikogovicu.

80
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:32,690
Nemoj da gledas prljavi nevernice.

81
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:36,000
Ostavljem te zauvek.

82
00:05:58,300 --> 00:06:00,300
Ja sam.

83
00:06:01,700 --> 00:06:03,700
Kako su svi?

84
00:06:03,700 --> 00:06:05,700
Spavaju.

85
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:09,900
Kako je Zimovka?

86
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:12,700
Umoran je. To mu
bila prva akcija.

87
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:15,520
Citao je "Monte Krista"
celu noc.

88
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:19,900
Dugo ti je trebalo da dodjes.
Sve je tu?

89
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,500
Da, poslat je telegram.

90
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:24,575
I soba u "Bristolu" je rezervisana.

91
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:28,400
Hvala na tacnosti. Covek
iz Odese stize

92
00:06:28,500 --> 00:06:30,600
prekosutra. Komitet.

93
00:06:31,700 --> 00:06:33,910
Doci ce po novac.
- Sjajno.

94
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,600
Sve je spremno.

95
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:42,200
Gde su mi sesiri?

96
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:51,445
Sve je zrtvovano na
oltaru revolucije.

97
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,700
Vreme je za pokret.

98
00:07:20,300 --> 00:07:22,600
Pa, gospodine Pozarski...

99
00:07:25,100 --> 00:07:27,300
Sada samo vam za petama.

100
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:30,300
A ostale sobe?

101
00:07:30,900 --> 00:07:34,470
Mozda odaberemo da
predjemo u neku od njih.

102
00:07:36,900 --> 00:07:38,900
Ona je?

103
00:08:08,300 --> 00:08:13,900
Soba 5. Kako ste?

104
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,800
Jedva nadjoh put.

105
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:23,800
Sampanjac! Uhvatili ste
Brigadire?

106
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:27,200
Ne jos. Skinite kaput.
Sampanjac?

107
00:08:27,300 --> 00:08:29,400
Ne, ne volim sampanjac.

108
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:33,500
Prava fontana.

109
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:37,400
Radije bih votku.

110
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:41,200
Da narucim? - Ne, u redu je.

111
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:45,405
Da li ste bili u parnom kupatilu?

112
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:50,500
Sjajno je ovde.

113
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:54,230
Nemamo takva
zadovoljstva u Petrogradu.

114
00:08:56,900 --> 00:08:59,000
Da pricamo oposlu.

115
00:08:59,900 --> 00:09:03,000
Hteli ste mi nesto reci, zar ne?

116
00:09:04,500 --> 00:09:06,500
Da.

117
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:14,800
Da li ste nasli izdajnika?

118
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:18,500
Ne jos.

119
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:22,500
Ali naci cu ga cu ga uskoro.

120
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:28,500
Ima ih troje.

121
00:09:30,300 --> 00:09:32,300
Idu ka sobi 5.

122
00:09:36,100 --> 00:09:38,100
Idemo.

123
00:09:45,300 --> 00:09:47,340
Trebalo bi da odmaglimo.

124
00:10:00,700 --> 00:10:02,700
Drugi je tvoj.

125
00:10:06,100 --> 00:10:08,100
Aleksej!

126
00:10:08,700 --> 00:10:10,700
Aleksej pomozi!

127
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:16,860
Pao je sa takve visine.
Vec je mrtav.

128
00:11:18,900 --> 00:11:22,500
Pijana svinjo.
Uhapsicu te.

129
00:12:05,300 --> 00:12:09,600
Nisi li ti spavalica?

130
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:12,440
Spavao si skoro 24 casa.

131
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:14,800
24 casa!

132
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:19,400
Mislio sam da si umro.
Lekar je rekao

133
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:23,655
da je nervni slom.
Hvala Bogu da ste citavi.

134
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:25,400
Citav.

135
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:29,100
Kako si pobegao?
- Smugnuo sam.

136
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:30,400
A vi?

137
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:33,500
Opet me spasila zena.
Gola zena.

138
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:37,600
Bilo je spektakularno.

139
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:41,800
Caj? - Da.

140
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:45,600
Poslednji put ste rekli

141
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,800
da imate trag Brigade,

142
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:52,035
zahvaljujuci meni. To je jedan.

143
00:12:52,700 --> 00:12:55,080
Sta je bilo juce? To je dva.

144
00:12:55,900 --> 00:12:58,200
Rekli ste: "Bez mene".

145
00:12:58,700 --> 00:13:01,165
Na sta ste mislili?
To je tri.

146
00:13:02,100 --> 00:13:04,100
Pre svega,

147
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:06,300
vi i ja cemo voditi

148
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:10,200
neobican... limun?

149
00:13:10,700 --> 00:13:14,355
...neobican komitet za
borbu protiv brigade.

150
00:13:14,700 --> 00:13:17,930
Odgovaracemo samo
njegovom velicanstvu.

151
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:21,000
I drugo:

152
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:25,400
Izgleda da sam nasao Brigadu.

153
00:13:26,700 --> 00:13:30,300
Kako vam je to uspelo?
- Preko vase Dijane.

154
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:33,700
Znate zasto vasa Dijana?

155
00:13:34,400 --> 00:13:36,400
Zato sto sam je

156
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:39,500
preko vas pronasao.

157
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:43,500
Da li se secate naseg razgovora
u plamenu baklji?

158
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:46,800
Videlo se da tajite nesto.

159
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:49,900
Zato sam vas posmatrao.

160
00:13:50,700 --> 00:13:53,100
Moji agenti su dojavili da

161
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:57,000
gospodin Fandorin posecuje
jednu vilu

162
00:13:57,700 --> 00:13:59,700
sa kupolom.

163
00:13:59,700 --> 00:14:01,900
Otisao sam tamo i
pritisnuo sarmantnu damu.

164
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:05,900
Dijana...

165
00:14:06,900 --> 00:14:10,100
Vi je poznajete kao Dijanu.

166
00:14:10,800 --> 00:14:13,010
Ali za Zelenog ona je DBD.

167
00:14:13,100 --> 00:14:15,100
DBD? - Upravo.

168
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:19,000
Smrtonosna Dijana
( Engl. Death Bringing Diana )

169
00:14:19,100 --> 00:14:21,700
Koja nas je sve zavlacila.
- Sacekajte.

170
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:23,400
Sacekajte, kako je
znala za sobu 5?

171
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:25,500
U sobi 3.

172
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:27,700
Oprostite, u sobi 5.

173
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:30,165
Gde je sada?
- Na istom mestu.

174
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:33,200
Cuvaju je moji agenti.
Ustajte Fandorine.

175
00:14:33,300 --> 00:14:35,100
Doneo sam vam vasu odecu.

176
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:37,920
Pokazacu vam nesto,
sacuvaj Boze,

177
00:14:38,100 --> 00:14:40,310
sto ni Dima ne bi smislio.

178
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:45,600
Pomozite gospodinu da se obuce.

179
00:14:50,400 --> 00:14:53,205
Prevideli ste!
- Vasa ekscelencijo

180
00:14:53,300 --> 00:14:57,550
rekli ste da ne ulazimo
i da je ne pustamo napolje.

181
00:15:03,100 --> 00:15:05,100
Spustite je.

182
00:15:11,900 --> 00:15:13,940
Makar je odradila svoje.

183
00:15:17,400 --> 00:15:20,630
Nesto mi je promaklo
u njenoj licnosti.

184
00:15:21,500 --> 00:15:26,400
Zasto tu stojite?

185
00:15:27,500 --> 00:15:29,800
Dodjite, ovo ce vam
biti interesantno.

186
00:15:29,900 --> 00:15:31,900
Spremni ste?

187
00:15:33,300 --> 00:15:35,600
Aplauz.

188
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:46,305
Sada znate zasto
je sedela u tami?

189
00:15:47,800 --> 00:15:50,800
Ocekivali ste nekog
drugog, zar ne?

190
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:55,050
Rekli ste da je obavila posao?

191
00:15:55,300 --> 00:15:57,700
Napisala je poruku

192
00:15:58,800 --> 00:16:00,500
koju sam joj izdiktirao:

193
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:03,660
"Sutra u podne ce
Fandorin i Pozarski

194
00:16:03,900 --> 00:16:07,900
doci u vrt Neskucni,

195
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:11,365
Ledeni lavirint".
Potpis: DBD.

196
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:15,600
Otici cete?
- Naravno.

197
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:19,100
Jasno je za Pozarskog.

198
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:21,800
Ali Fandorin...

199
00:16:22,500 --> 00:16:24,500
Emilija!

200
00:16:29,700 --> 00:16:31,700
Rece da je Fandorin mrtav?

201
00:16:31,800 --> 00:16:35,800
Ziv je i sastaje se
sa Pozarskim sutra.

202
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:38,500
Nemoj mi reci!
- Da!

203
00:16:42,300 --> 00:16:44,300
Za ime Bozije!

204
00:16:44,700 --> 00:16:47,200
Njemu se bas ne umire.
Bomba bi to resila.

205
00:16:47,300 --> 00:16:49,300
Do vraga, nema fitilja.

206
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:52,150
Toliko dinamita
a nema fitilja.

207
00:17:01,800 --> 00:17:05,500
Imamo parafin i destilator
kao i staklene cevi...

208
00:17:05,600 --> 00:17:08,900
Mogli bi da napravimo
zele bombu.

209
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:13,210
Ali nemamo nitroglicerina.

210
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:17,500
Mogli bismo da potrazimo
u Aronzonovoj laboratoriji.

211
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:19,810
Sta ako ga je Rahmet odao?

212
00:17:20,500 --> 00:17:22,795
Provericemo. Zovi Aronzona.

213
00:17:24,700 --> 00:17:26,700
Sigurno ce doci.

214
00:17:27,100 --> 00:17:29,800
U tom trenu moji Ijudi
i ja se pojavljujemo:

215
00:17:29,900 --> 00:17:33,200
Reci cu im da moraju da se
predaju sto oni nece uciniti.

216
00:17:33,300 --> 00:17:36,200
Vi cete skociti u skroviste
pa cemo ih poseci.

217
00:17:36,300 --> 00:17:38,700
Skroviste?

218
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:41,400
Dragi Eraste,

219
00:17:41,500 --> 00:17:44,800
o svemu sam mislio.

220
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:48,200
Da li si to ti Semjone?

221
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:51,400
Da li si dobro?

222
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:55,000
Mozemo li da dodjemo do tebe?

223
00:17:57,100 --> 00:18:00,840
Probudio sam ga. Stizem.
- Ne, idemo zajedno.

224
00:18:07,700 --> 00:18:09,740
Sta mislite o mom planu?

225
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:12,210
Dobar plan sa malo rizika.

226
00:18:12,600 --> 00:18:15,200
Da igramo u cetiri ruke?

227
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:27,900
Da li ste stvarno mislili

228
00:18:28,300 --> 00:18:30,765
da bih vas poslao na metkove?

229
00:18:30,900 --> 00:18:32,900
Idemo.

230
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:37,300
Ti udji i pogledaj kroz prozor.

231
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:41,800
Ako ne pogledas u roku
od tri minuta znacice da je zaseda.

232
00:18:41,900 --> 00:18:43,940
U tom slicaju odmah idi.

233
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:47,580
Mozes da osanes u skladistu.

234
00:18:49,900 --> 00:18:52,200
Necu te izdati. - Znam.

235
00:18:55,300 --> 00:18:58,200
Nece me muciti, zar ne?

236
00:18:59,600 --> 00:19:01,600
Tri minuta!

237
00:20:00,500 --> 00:20:02,500
Sutov! Ko je tamo?

238
00:20:04,100 --> 00:20:06,100
Sedi s mirom kucko.

239
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:11,200
Imala sam vremena

240
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:14,300
da prbusim grlo iglom,

241
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:17,900
ali nisam mogla.

242
00:20:19,900 --> 00:20:21,900
Izvini.

243
00:20:22,700 --> 00:20:25,675
Dobro je, zasto bih
inace rizikovao.

244
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:30,000
To je bio

245
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:33,100
Krapovljev sef garde.

246
00:20:34,100 --> 00:20:36,100
Poludeo je.

247
00:20:36,600 --> 00:20:38,700
Ubio je Aronzona.

248
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:43,200
Mozda je tako najbolje.

249
00:20:57,900 --> 00:20:59,900
Prebili su me.

250
00:21:00,300 --> 00:21:02,300
Sada sam tako ruzna.

251
00:21:08,800 --> 00:21:10,800
Ne,

252
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:14,800
veoma si lepa.

253
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:37,195
Zaklela sam se sebi ali...
To je sve besmisleno.

254
00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:39,300
Besmisleno.

255
00:21:39,900 --> 00:21:42,500
Naravno da jeste...

256
00:22:04,100 --> 00:22:06,800
U vrtu ce biti ledena tvrdjava.

257
00:22:08,300 --> 00:22:10,340
I klupa, desno od ulaza.

258
00:22:10,900 --> 00:22:14,000
Trebalo bi da sednete...

259
00:22:14,500 --> 00:22:17,700
Sa vase desne strane bice rupa,

260
00:22:18,400 --> 00:22:20,700
rupa u snegu.

261
00:22:22,100 --> 00:22:24,300
Tu treba da upadnete.

262
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:27,495
Dole je rov, ici cete njime

263
00:22:27,600 --> 00:22:30,000
sve do susedne ulice.

264
00:22:30,600 --> 00:22:35,100
Trebalo bi da nestanete
pre nego sto pocne pucnjava.

265
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:37,700
Moglo bi biti opasno.

266
00:24:27,100 --> 00:24:29,100
Pucaj!

267
00:24:38,300 --> 00:24:40,300
Trci!@ Emilija!

268
00:24:54,900 --> 00:24:57,000
Ubili su Zimovku!

269
00:25:15,700 --> 00:25:17,700
Ne!

270
00:25:28,300 --> 00:25:31,400
Da li ste vi ludi?

271
00:25:31,900 --> 00:25:34,700
Zasto niste skocili u rupu?

272
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:37,400
Mogli su vas ubiti.

273
00:25:37,500 --> 00:25:41,240
Nisu da su citali Silera
ili o Vilijemu Telu.

274
00:25:43,900 --> 00:25:45,900
Skocio sam.

275
00:25:46,500 --> 00:25:48,500
O Boze!

276
00:25:53,600 --> 00:25:56,300
Ko je ovo ucinio?

277
00:26:07,600 --> 00:26:10,300
Sta? - Mrtvi su.

278
00:26:11,500 --> 00:26:13,795
Emilija i Zimovka su mrtvi.

279
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:26,400
Policija ce ovamo svaki cas.
Trebalo bi da bezimo.

280
00:26:35,700 --> 00:26:38,000
Ali gde?

281
00:26:40,500 --> 00:26:42,600
Mojoj kuci.

282
00:26:47,100 --> 00:26:49,100
Brigada je unistena.

283
00:26:49,500 --> 00:26:53,240
Osim sefa sto znaci...
- Pozarski nije uspeo.

284
00:26:53,400 --> 00:26:54,900
Brooj jedan:

285
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:57,800
Izvesticu o nestaslucima Pozarskog.

286
00:26:57,900 --> 00:27:00,300
I on ce dobiti svoje
lupkanje po guzi.

287
00:27:00,400 --> 00:27:02,400
Sta mislite koga cu

288
00:27:02,600 --> 00:27:04,600
naciniti briznikom

289
00:27:05,600 --> 00:27:07,700
sefa moskovske policije?

290
00:27:08,300 --> 00:27:10,850
Vas Fandorine.
- Nece odobriti.

291
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:12,900
Hoce, tim pre sto

292
00:27:13,500 --> 00:27:16,200
cemo im dati Zelenog
na tacni.

293
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:21,110
Idite sada da uzmete
kancelariju u rezidenciji.

294
00:27:33,100 --> 00:27:35,820
Moje cestitke vasa ekscelencijo.

295
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:38,400
Vasa studija jos nije spremna.

296
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:40,500
Ali bice uskoro.

297
00:27:40,500 --> 00:27:42,500
Hitno je.

298
00:27:43,600 --> 00:27:47,100
Lice Nikanora Kabilkina.

299
00:27:49,100 --> 00:27:51,100
Sta se desava?

300
00:27:51,100 --> 00:27:53,400
Vasi licni strazari, najbolji.

301
00:27:53,500 --> 00:27:56,475
Najbolji bi trebalo
da jure bandite.

302
00:27:56,900 --> 00:27:58,900
Mozete ici.

303
00:28:00,500 --> 00:28:02,500
Eraste Petrovicu.

304
00:28:04,900 --> 00:28:06,900
Dobar dan.

305
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:10,740
Mislio sam da samo
petrogradjani vole reforme

306
00:28:11,300 --> 00:28:14,200
ali izgleda da i moskovljani
imaju istu manu.

307
00:28:14,300 --> 00:28:17,955
Zauzet sam. Ali ako
imate vesti o Brigadi...

308
00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:21,800
Nemam vesti o VB

309
00:28:22,500 --> 00:28:25,500
ali imam o GG,

310
00:28:26,500 --> 00:28:28,800
Mislim na sebe.

311
00:28:32,500 --> 00:28:36,000
Evo dekreta njegovog velicanstva.

312
00:28:36,700 --> 00:28:38,700
o mom postavljenju

313
00:28:38,900 --> 00:28:41,400
na mesto sefa moskovske policije.

314
00:28:41,500 --> 00:28:44,220
Znaci, vase reforme su poranile.

315
00:28:44,300 --> 00:28:46,300
Salim se.

316
00:28:46,500 --> 00:28:49,560
Samo moj zastitnik ima ostrije zube.

317
00:28:55,100 --> 00:28:57,100
Sada probajte ovo

318
00:28:58,600 --> 00:29:00,600
da uradite sami.

319
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:19,240
Obesen je pre tri godine
u Jekaterinoslavlju.

320
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:23,400
Ko je onda DBD?

321
00:29:23,900 --> 00:29:25,900
Ko?

322
00:29:29,800 --> 00:29:32,435
Prvo nam pomaze a posle izdaje.

323
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:34,700
Ne razumem.

324
00:29:34,800 --> 00:29:36,800
Recite mi,

325
00:29:37,900 --> 00:29:40,700
da li ste ikada voleli?

326
00:29:43,400 --> 00:29:45,400
Stavite eksere.

327
00:29:45,700 --> 00:29:48,250
Ne secam se,
sve je besmisleno.

328
00:29:51,500 --> 00:29:54,300
Nije trenutak za ovo.

329
00:29:55,700 --> 00:29:57,700
Naravno,

330
00:29:58,700 --> 00:30:01,800
Ijubav nije nista,
ima vaznijih stvari.

331
00:30:01,900 --> 00:30:03,900
Pazljivo.

332
00:30:04,300 --> 00:30:06,400
Jos jedan.

333
00:30:08,800 --> 00:30:10,800
Ukrsteno.

334
00:30:25,900 --> 00:30:27,900
DBD...

335
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:30,000
Kako da ga pronadjemo?

336
00:30:30,100 --> 00:30:32,990
Kako su poruke stigle?
- Razlicito.

337
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:39,075
Poslednji put kada sam
video Zuli i tu poruku bilo je...

338
00:30:40,900 --> 00:30:43,700
Naravno!

339
00:30:44,700 --> 00:30:46,825
U Petrogradu, u Moskvi...

340
00:30:57,200 --> 00:30:59,400
Dajte mi hotel Bristol.

341
00:31:00,800 --> 00:31:03,095
Postoji vaznije naredjenje:

342
00:31:03,900 --> 00:31:07,700
Grof Dugalski bi trebalo
da da ostavku,

343
00:31:08,700 --> 00:31:10,800
sa pocastima i ceremonijom.

344
00:31:10,900 --> 00:31:13,450
A moskovski gubernator bice...

345
00:31:13,500 --> 00:31:16,700
brat njegovog velicanstva,

346
00:31:17,900 --> 00:31:20,000
veliki vojvoda Simon.

347
00:31:20,700 --> 00:31:22,700
Razumete?

348
00:31:23,700 --> 00:31:25,910
Ne razumem zasto ovo rade?

349
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:28,500
Dolglrutski je star ali iskusan.

350
00:31:28,600 --> 00:31:32,300
Nece biti problema
pod njim u Moskvi.

351
00:31:35,300 --> 00:31:37,935
Vi zapravo imate
andjeosko srce.

352
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:42,600
Nema problema, to je poenta.

353
00:31:43,100 --> 00:31:46,160
Osoba bez problema
je veliki problem.

354
00:31:47,100 --> 00:31:50,200
Ni caru ni nama

355
00:31:50,800 --> 00:31:53,000
ne treba takva osoba.

356
00:31:53,500 --> 00:31:56,000
Treba im komedijas.

357
00:31:56,800 --> 00:31:58,800
Recimo glumac Sapkin,
nema bi bradu ni brkova da povucete.

358
00:31:58,900 --> 00:32:00,900
Problemi su kao brada:

359
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:05,450
Mozete ih vuci, mozete
coveka da vucarate za bradu.

360
00:32:07,300 --> 00:32:09,300
Treba mi savet.

361
00:32:24,500 --> 00:32:28,100
Odakle zovete?

362
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:30,700
Da, ovaj broj.

363
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:34,900
Shvatam.

364
00:32:46,800 --> 00:32:48,800
U redu.

365
00:32:50,100 --> 00:32:53,415
Zbogom Fandorine,
razgovaracemo kasnije.

366
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:58,000
Da li su savetnikove
sanke jos uvek pred ulazom?

367
00:32:58,100 --> 00:33:01,160
Da gospodine.
- Nemojte ih otpustati.

368
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:04,300
Zeleni je u zamci.

369
00:33:04,900 --> 00:33:06,900
Ali bez vase saradnje.

370
00:33:07,100 --> 00:33:09,400
Gospodine...
- Gospodine...

371
00:33:26,500 --> 00:33:29,305
Gde biste isli?
- Koliko su sanke?

372
00:33:29,900 --> 00:33:31,900
Koliko za sanke?

373
00:33:32,900 --> 00:33:35,500
Znatan je, da se menjamo?

374
00:33:35,900 --> 00:33:38,000
Hajde. - Au.

375
00:33:49,100 --> 00:33:51,100
Da li ste ozbiljni?

376
00:33:51,500 --> 00:33:53,500
Hotel Bristol.

377
00:34:27,200 --> 00:34:29,200
Sacekajte ovde.

378
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:49,900
Rekao je da je hitno.

379
00:34:50,400 --> 00:34:53,100
Rekao je vozi niz
ulicu Mjasnickaja.

380
00:34:53,200 --> 00:34:56,000
Plasi se da ga neko ne prati.
Da li je sumnjicav?

381
00:34:56,100 --> 00:34:58,200
Brines za mene, zar ne?

382
00:34:59,100 --> 00:35:04,000
Dragi glebe, to je
uobicajena obazrivost.

383
00:35:08,700 --> 00:35:11,930
Ti si moja talija.
- A ti moj pobednik.

384
00:35:18,900 --> 00:35:20,900
Kasnim, zdravo.

385
00:35:21,700 --> 00:35:23,500
Vidimo se uskoro.

386
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:26,000
Uskoro, da.

387
00:35:27,300 --> 00:35:29,300
Idemo.

388
00:35:33,000 --> 00:35:35,200
Pogledaj me.

389
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:40,000
Secas se Strelnje?

390
00:35:40,500 --> 00:35:43,200
Reci mi. - Dosta.

391
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:58,600
Cekacu da cujem rec od tebe.

392
00:36:04,200 --> 00:36:06,200
Idimo sporije.

393
00:36:14,900 --> 00:36:17,300
Sta zelis? - On mi je prijatelj.

394
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:20,000
Kako si Zeleni?
- Idi pravo.

395
00:37:12,100 --> 00:37:15,075
Molim? Jel' to
neka manija gonjenja?

396
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:17,695
Nisam videla nikakvo pismo.

397
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:21,400
Nisam ni gledala u vrata.
Zurila sam da te vidim.

398
00:37:21,500 --> 00:37:25,200
Vidjena si kod Bristola
u drustvu Pozarskog.

399
00:37:39,300 --> 00:37:42,020
Koliko dugo si policijski agent?

400
00:37:43,200 --> 00:37:45,200
Ali zasto?

401
00:37:47,600 --> 00:37:49,900
Ubicu te ako ne progovoris.

402
00:37:50,500 --> 00:37:53,600
Govoris - zivis.
- Da, ja sam agent.

403
00:37:54,100 --> 00:37:56,100
Od samog pocetka.

404
00:37:56,200 --> 00:37:57,400
O Boze...

405
00:37:57,500 --> 00:37:59,710
On je diktirao sve poruke.

406
00:38:03,100 --> 00:38:05,100
Ko?

407
00:38:05,600 --> 00:38:07,600
Ko?

408
00:38:10,500 --> 00:38:12,500
Pozarski?

409
00:38:16,700 --> 00:38:18,700
Zasto? - Ne znam.

410
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:21,800
Nije moja stvar.

411
00:38:22,700 --> 00:38:25,080
Sve je to samo decacka igra.

412
00:38:25,300 --> 00:38:27,510
Zovi svog dobrotvora.
- Ne.

413
00:38:33,700 --> 00:38:35,900
Ubices me, zar ne?

414
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:38,400
U redu.

415
00:38:38,900 --> 00:38:41,025
Obecaj da ces me pustiti.

416
00:38:42,900 --> 00:38:46,300
Hocu kada sve sa Pozarskim
bude zavrseno.

417
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:53,400
Kancelarija sefa policije?

418
00:38:53,900 --> 00:38:58,700
Moram hitno da govorim sa grofom.

419
00:38:59,300 --> 00:39:01,300
Zuli je.

420
00:39:03,900 --> 00:39:06,700
Hvala. Nije stigao.

421
00:39:09,300 --> 00:39:11,400
Sacekacemo onda.

422
00:39:14,400 --> 00:39:17,200
Zvaces za 15 minuta.

423
00:39:28,200 --> 00:39:30,800
Sedi.

424
00:39:45,800 --> 00:39:48,100
Kocija gospodine?
- Dosao sam sankama.

425
00:39:48,200 --> 00:39:51,200
Pricacemo kasnije.
Sada je kljucan momenat.

426
00:39:51,300 --> 00:39:53,300
Vas kljucan momenat.

427
00:39:57,700 --> 00:40:00,300
Sjaj u tvojim ocima i to crvenilo.

428
00:40:00,400 --> 00:40:05,500
Sta se dogodilo gospodine Statuo?
Da li ste uhvatili Zelenog?

429
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:08,100
Nekoga vaznijeg.

430
00:40:12,300 --> 00:40:15,400
U redu, imate pet minuta.

431
00:40:16,500 --> 00:40:20,400
Pomozi mi sa kaputom.

432
00:40:23,700 --> 00:40:25,700
Odlazite.

433
00:40:26,200 --> 00:40:28,200
Gospode, jos ste tu

434
00:40:31,600 --> 00:40:33,725
Ti nisi samo karijerista.

435
00:40:34,100 --> 00:40:36,800
Ti si provokator,
drzavni kriminalac.

436
00:40:36,900 --> 00:40:39,600
Ti stojis iza Brigade.
Hoces Dokaze?

437
00:40:39,700 --> 00:40:43,015
Ne, sada ces se ulenjiti
i saviti prste:

438
00:40:43,100 --> 00:40:46,585
ovo je prvo, ovo je drugo,
ono je trece...

439
00:40:47,200 --> 00:40:49,240
Ali nemam vremena za to.

440
00:40:49,700 --> 00:40:52,165
Moram ovo sto pre da zavrsim.

441
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:56,900
Mislis da sam vodja terorista, pa sta?

442
00:40:57,600 --> 00:40:59,400
Kako to "pa sta"?

443
00:40:59,500 --> 00:41:02,700
Sta imate protiv mene?

444
00:41:03,500 --> 00:41:06,400
Dedukcione ideje?
Ja ne ostavljam tragove.

445
00:41:06,500 --> 00:41:10,155
Svako normalan ce
reci da je obo besmislica.

446
00:41:10,200 --> 00:41:14,600
Niko vam nece verovati.
A sto se tice dedukcije zabijte je...

447
00:41:14,700 --> 00:41:17,400
u novcanik.

448
00:41:24,200 --> 00:41:25,700
Ne mogu da verujem.

449
00:41:25,800 --> 00:41:27,800
Recite mi,

450
00:41:28,300 --> 00:41:30,800
sta ce vam sva ta ruznoca?

451
00:41:32,600 --> 00:41:36,800
Za ime Bozije,

452
00:41:37,300 --> 00:41:40,275
ne nazivajte patriotski cin ruznim.

453
00:41:40,500 --> 00:41:42,795
Ovo je vama patriotski cin?

454
00:41:43,300 --> 00:41:45,340
Upravo dragi prijatelju.

455
00:41:46,500 --> 00:41:48,700
Imam dve vrste neprijatelja:

456
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:50,840
glupane koji na polozaju

457
00:41:51,300 --> 00:41:54,100
koji ce unistiti drzavni
aparat iznutra

458
00:41:54,200 --> 00:41:57,200
i teroriste koji ce to uciniti spolja.

459
00:41:57,300 --> 00:41:59,425
Ne znam koji su opasniji.

460
00:41:59,900 --> 00:42:02,195
A nemamo vremena Fandorine.

461
00:42:02,600 --> 00:42:05,000
Za dve godine unistice Rusiju.

462
00:42:05,100 --> 00:42:07,100
I zato vi... - Da.

463
00:42:08,900 --> 00:42:10,900
Da!

464
00:42:11,100 --> 00:42:12,900
Zato

465
00:42:13,000 --> 00:42:15,000
koristim pamet,

466
00:42:15,100 --> 00:42:17,200
talnat i hrabrost,

467
00:42:17,900 --> 00:42:19,900
i industriju

468
00:42:20,900 --> 00:42:25,800
da stvorim komplikovani
mehanizam.

469
00:42:27,100 --> 00:42:30,100
Radio je tiho, bez greske.

470
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:34,800
Kao ovaj sat,

471
00:42:35,400 --> 00:42:37,780
poklon njegovog velicanstva.

472
00:42:38,200 --> 00:42:42,705
Zeleni e bio moj instrument
u ciscenju puta za Rusiju:

473
00:42:44,200 --> 00:42:47,000
i nasta manje glupana

474
00:42:48,100 --> 00:42:50,100
a vazduh je postao cistiji.

475
00:42:50,200 --> 00:42:54,100
Onaj ko uhvati Brigadu

476
00:42:55,500 --> 00:42:58,475
koje se svi plase
moze sve da trazi.

477
00:42:58,700 --> 00:43:00,995
I moze da uzme koliko hoce.

478
00:43:02,000 --> 00:43:04,400
Cega? - Bilo cega.

479
00:43:04,800 --> 00:43:06,800
Novca, moci.

480
00:43:07,900 --> 00:43:09,900
A ako mu ne daju?

481
00:43:12,500 --> 00:43:15,600
Onda ce se pojaviti druga Brigada.

482
00:43:17,100 --> 00:43:19,500
Jos opasnija.

483
00:43:22,500 --> 00:43:25,560
Vi onda cistite put sebi
a ne Rusiji.

484
00:43:26,300 --> 00:43:29,600
Za razliku od vas, Rusija je deo mene.

485
00:43:30,300 --> 00:43:32,850
Sta valja rusiji valja i meni.

486
00:43:33,300 --> 00:43:35,300
I obratno, nadam se.

487
00:43:37,700 --> 00:43:39,825
Ne mogu vam to dopustiti.

488
00:43:40,300 --> 00:43:42,850
Ne date mi da uhvatim Zelenog?

489
00:43:44,900 --> 00:43:47,025
Ne dam vam da prevladate.

490
00:43:47,200 --> 00:43:49,300
Vi ste djavo.

491
00:43:54,200 --> 00:43:56,200
Kasno je.

492
00:43:57,500 --> 00:43:59,540
Gospodine Eraste Fauste.

493
00:43:59,800 --> 00:44:01,800
Prekasno.

